<p>Now the directories are set up correctly, but there is still some work to do. Check out the
   following sections for more details:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="templates" title="Create the templates">Create</a> the templates required for displaying your site.</li>
  <li><a href="config" title="Configure the site">Configure</a> the site options and register pages.</li>
  <li><a href="content" title="Create content">Add</a> and organize your content.</li>
</ul>
